// ## Dependencies to Install
// npm install node-appwrite        # Appwrite server SDK
// npm install react-dropzone       # File upload drag-and-drop
// npm install recharts             # Dashboard storage chart
// npm install clsx tailwind-merge  # cn() utility
// npm install tailwindcss-animate  # ShadCN animations

// //